    "description": """
      <h3>Activation:</h3>
      <p>As an Attack and Scheme action using a readied melee weapon or unarmed, you may make a <strong>Blades or Hand-to-Hand check</strong> targeting one character at range 0. The TN is equal to the target's Vigilance, reduced to 1 if either character is currently in Dangerous, Entangling, or Obscuring terrain.</p>
      <h3>Effects:</h3>
      <p>If you succeed, your target suffers the Prone condition and fatigue equal to your ranks in Conditioning.</p>
      <h3>New Opportunities:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Power (op)(op):</strong> Your target suffers the Immobilized condition instead of Prone.</li>
      </ul>
    """
  },
