      <ul>
        <li><strong>Power (op)+:</strong> Your target must resist with a <strong>TN 3 Conditioning check (Swiftness 1, Resilience 2)</strong>, plus 1 to all TNs per additional Power (op) spent this way. If they fail, they suffer the Dazed condition and fatigue equal to their shortfall.</li>
      </ul>
    """
